{"tid":320491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸要拍動畫《哪吒與變形金剛》 ，中美雙方已達版權共識","createTime":"2017-07-13T14:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T15:53:24.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b815612d7ff4ccdde675980fb566352309c98093","tid":320491,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"據大陸央視網稱，近日，美國孩之寶公司全球CEO史蒂芬&middot;戴維斯等一行10人到央視動畫有限公司，就合拍動畫項目《哪吒與變形金剛》進行洽談，並就製作規格、播出時間、知識產權歸屬、法律事務等方面達成共識。<br />\n   報導指出，雙方還表示，期待建立更加穩固的戰略合作夥伴關係，深度挖掘經典動畫IP的品牌價值，進一步激發既有動畫IP的品牌活力。報導說，《哪吒與變形金剛》項目是中美動畫合作領域的里程碑項目。<br />\n  報導說，此前，央視動畫就發行、授權及衍生品開發等事項與美方進行多輪溝通，積極推進該項目的合作與落地。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170713005434-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170713005434-260409&d=IKE5B3xalFjF69%2F32X2WuYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fb59ec3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170713005434-260409</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/222652_fabf4ee998af2934ed045eb7537e5ad0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F222652_fabf4ee998af2934ed045eb7537e5ad0.jpg&h=3ea20bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於可以看到哪叱用五味真火對抗柯柏文"},{"pid":"bb3d9c8b51291e9dc39fb130cb417f215fa82a31","tid":320491,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:29:22.000Z","msg":"將軍澳果邊咪有囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba86f757b2a6d8fa2ec2ab83d35f3d60f17a58f1","tid":320491,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n吹水咋話"},{"pid":"9af2d7a673bacf00e3514a0c92f375429b225cda","tid":320491,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead